                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Dures grenades entr’ouvertes\nCédant à l’excès de vos grains,\nJe crois voir des fronts souverains\nÉclatés de leurs découvertes !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Si les soleils par vous subis,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Ô grenades entre-bâillées",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Vous ont fait d’orgueil travaillées",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Craquer les cloisons de rubis,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Si les soleils par vous subis,\nÔ grenades entre-bâillées\nVous ont fait d’orgueil travaillées\nCraquer les cloisons de rubis,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Et que si l’or sec de l’écorce",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "À la demande d’une force",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "e"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Crève en gemmes rouges de jus,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "f"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et que si l’or sec de l’écorce\nÀ la demande d’une force\nCrève en gemmes rouges de jus,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Cette lumineuse rupture",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "g"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Fait rêver une âme que j’eus",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "f"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "De sa secrète architecture.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "g"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Cette lumineuse rupture\nFait rêver une âme que j’eus\nDe sa secrète architecture."
        }
